// Apple Developer Team ID template.
//
// One-time setup:
//   cp ios/team.xcconfig.example ios/team.xcconfig
//   # Then edit ios/team.xcconfig and fill in DEVELOPMENT_TEAM below.
//
// Find your Team ID at https://developer.apple.com/account → Membership.
// It is a 10-character alphanumeric identifier (e.g. ABCDE12345).
//
// ios/team.xcconfig is gitignored. It is included by ios/debug.xcconfig via
// `#include? "team.xcconfig"` so the project picks it up automatically the
// next time Xcode opens. With CODE_SIGN_STYLE = Automatic (set in the
// .pbxproj), Xcode uses this team ID to provision a development certificate
// the first time you build for a device.

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =
